### NOTES FOR TESTING:
### 1. Check application console/debug output for detailed logs
### 2. Logs should show: HTTP method, path, status code, elapsed time
### 3. Authentication errors should return 401 Unauthorized
### 4. Validation errors should return 400 Bad Request with detailed error messages
### 5. All error responses should follow the standardized JSON format
### 6. Health check endpoint should NOT require authentication
### 7. Swagger endpoints should NOT require authentication
